<cl=A2A2A2>
Druids represent the most ancient school of magic in Sphere. Druids' entire life is dedicated to searching for harmony with nature, so military skills and flashy titles are alien to druids. The destructive elements such as fire and air are not highly appreciated in this guild, but they spend much time studying the magic of earth and water. Druids live in the forest and have conceived many of its secrets. Forests are quite dangerous in Sphere, so druids have mastered the art of protection from military attacks perfectly. Brute force is not is not what they are good at though, and Druids prefer to attack using magic which grows with each new stage thanks to the Guilds's secrets. Druids are the only magicians in Sphere who have mastered, over years of hard work, the language and magic of animals. Their efforts have not been wasted though, as each druid can now call an animal for help when in need and even turn into a wolf. Despite such power the Druids guild is not warlike and prefers to gain laurels as a guild of skillful healers and alchemists.
<br>
